    <item>
      <title>如果勒庞领导的政党赢得大选，法国绿色能源转型将面临停滞的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/france-s-green-energy-shift-at-risk-of-stalling-if-le-pen-s-party-wins-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国扩大可再生能源、摆脱化石燃料的计划正面临玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼民族主义政党的威胁，该政党可能会在数周内的立法选举中赢得最多席位，并废除关键的环境政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/france-s-green-energy-shift-at-risk-of-stalling-if-le-pen-s-party-wins-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平表示，军队整顿仍是中国首要任务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/xi-calls-for-greater-loyalty-and-discipline-in-china-s-military</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国领导人习近平表示，他将推进中国历史上最大规模的反腐风暴之一，并在一次罕见的军队会议上呼吁军队“深刻反思”，以确保军队忠诚卫国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/xi-calls-for-greater-loyalty-and-discipline-in-china-s-military</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 11:58:43 GMT</pubDate>
